==English==
===Etymology===
From the surname of [[w:John Wayne Bobbitt|John Wayne Bobbitt]], whose wife cut off his penis during his sleep.

===Transitive verb===
'''Bobbitt''' ('''Bobbitts''', '''Bobbitting''', '''Bobbitted''', '''Bobbittized''')

# {{informal}} To cut off the [[penis]] of (a man).
#:''Watch out, she might bobbitt you as you sleep.''